{"tid":1694582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳肇始：當局將發建議教市民如何處理接觸催淚彈後不適","createTime":"2019-11-05T08:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T11:05:16.000Z","uid":1121,"like":23,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"4ae411b8d81fe4728a7048ee692eba2b2257c178","tid":1694582,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局局長陳肇始出席活動後，被問到警方近日多次在民居施放催淚彈，導致市民不適。她表示，十分關注市民因吸入催淚煙後影響健康。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始說，衞生部門掌握的資料有限，但在參考相關文獻及了解催淚煙的情況後，衞生署將會發放，教導市民如何應付接觸催淚彈後不適的建議，市民或會出現短暫的不適，如眼睛刺痛、流眼水及嘔吐。<br />\n<br />\n她又指出，接觸後出現的不適情況，視乎個人健康情況、化學成份及曝露於催淚氣體的時間長度而定，難以一概而論，呼籲市民如果出現持續不適，應諮詢醫護人員建議。"},{"pid":"3be8b7b359a44d7887b01a147955d31fa1c6ec60","tid":1694582,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:20:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"065db9e6634d0740c78c299eb987f175ed508d35","tid":1694582,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490192-20191105.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR1f2O7LwdYFsQrAUI8ZkJZtjlaeVPV2rln7IAT1avNBJg-CvG09PVXPkhs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490192-20191105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR1f2O7LwdYFsQrAUI8ZkJZtjlaeVPV2rln7IAT1avNBJg-CvG09PVXPkhs&d=kDaEa4B9Gv5qH72Sa3%2FdwG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=51a491f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1490192-20191105.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0%26fbclid%3DIwAR1f2O7LwdYFsQrAUI8ZkJZtjlaeVPV2rln7IAT1avNBJg-CvG09PVXPkhs&h=ae2f92a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1490192-20191105.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwAR1f2O7LwdYFsQrAUI8ZkJZtjlaeVPV2rln7IAT1avNBJg-CvG09PVXPkhs</a>"},{"pid":"bc793399e8de1006e9b5df2be5342b3849353a94","tid":1694582,"uid":215876,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"4ae411b8d81fe4728a7048ee